A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of input text","type":"text"}]},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"input text"}]},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTextInput"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTextInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"TextInputComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"input text","type":"text"}]},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Inout text"}]},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of colors (","type":"text"},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":